<p><em>Overview:</em></p>
<p>The Zen Shortcode plugin is an updated version of our original JB Type plugin. Zen Shortcode has been specifically designed for use with the Zen Grid Framework v4. If you are using a template that is not compatible with Zen Grid Framework v4 please use the JB Type plugin in order to render functionality similar to the examples below.</p>";